0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T02:47:33.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"f843298dbb1a99b7bcaa147e826ab74a0270fa29","tid":1975910,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:47:33.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"f65c63794dc404d9324c62b5522a4378fe29d28a","tid":1975910,"uid":40542,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:49:42.000Z","msg":"上庭手足要人<br />\n保釋手足要遮陣<br />\n還押手足要送車"},{"pid":"4b16af19d2e239e8382308af7c3a8dd99504aa73","tid":1975910,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:53:47.000Z","msg":"推到俾區議員見到"},{"pid":"2cca1625f443d0b8c99f8d8466859b1a7f71c45f","tid":1975910,"uid":14361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:55:12.000Z","msg":"推呀！！"},{"pid":"2c1f22979bab949530eaddb26a9a10c49d50d4e5","tid":1975910,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T03:59:56.000Z","msg":"再推吓先"},{"pid":"dcb0fcd7a0cc9284d28f9f3ce125565a33e7f592","tid":1975910,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:08:10.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞係恐怖分子嚟<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1976085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1976085</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e423a91e3c140e9b722d361332c61fd8f26fb7cc","tid":1975910,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:13:30.000Z","msg":"#區域法院第三十五庭<br />\n#郭偉健法官<br />\n#提訊<br />\n<br />\n👥張,胡,陳,蘇,李(17-25) （#1001銅鑼灣 串謀縱火:白電油、打火機等）<br />\n👤沈(24)（#1001銅鑼灣 串謀縱火）<br />\n<br />\n2020年2月13日控方已遞交合併申請，全體辯方不反對<br />\n<br />\n法庭批准DCCC908/2019 將與 DCCC918/2019合併處理<br />\n<br />\n控罪：串謀縱火<br />\n<br />\n案情：10月1日反送中示威遍地開花，警方當日凌晨根據線報，到銅鑼灣一個單位內拘捕多人，搜出白電油、玻璃瓶、布條、防毒面具等物品。第一被告先被控串謀暴動，及後才修改為串謀縱火。<br />\n<br />\n答辯意向<br />\nA1 張<br />\nA2 胡<br />\nA3 陳<br />\nA4 蘇<br />\nA5 李<br />\nA6 沈<br />\n<br />\n全體被告不認罪<br />\n<br />\n案件進程<br />\n<br />\n2020年10月5日0930審前覆核<br />\n<br />\n2020年11月30日0930開審連續18個工作天至12月23日進行正式審訊<br />\n<br />\n其間以原有條件擔保"},{"pid":"2b927a3bd95cf4c491903122bfb82e938f3f1857","tid":1975910,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:23:57.000Z","msg":"多啲留意被捕組🙇&zwj;♀👇<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/13733\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk%2F13733&d=74s%2FNZguDZpTF4W18ni10Jq%2FK6ZSh20SQa5bazxoXL8%3D&h=46dee370\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk/13733</a><br />\n<br />\n🟥1⃣🟥97旺角20歲梁義士POOW還押至今至少20日。判刑🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥<br />\n🔴2⃣0205油麻地酒店案23歲陳義士還押至今至少65日。被威迫簽口供紙，否則會「搞死」他。<br />\n🔴3⃣0122屯門32歲李義士被捕2次（旺角非法集結），還押至今至少80日。<br />\n🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥🟥<br />\n4⃣國殤銅鑼灣張、胡、陳、蘇、李義士（17-25歲）。23歲義士被捕兩次（93黃大仙42C巴士）<br />\n#42C係紅媒01篤灰<br />\n5⃣國殤銅鑼灣24歲沈義士<br />\n<br />\n6⃣1202旺角16歲尼泊爾義士<br />\n7⃣922屯門64歲莊義士<br />\n8⃣1118理大圍城尖沙咀，20個義士（16-44歲）"},{"pid":"288279dd5b36aa7f9bf02e4f33e48a0f653f6e8d","tid":1975910,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:30:52.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"6aa73c800cf502b8bfd804944efe60bbb1ea6f7f","tid":1975910,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:31:02.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"fef4a3609cc5b87f9f8662d3789cccfab84d2346","tid":1975910,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T04:43:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ee21e4c8a3bf43fa9172824d8cb11ddba09bf02","tid":1975910,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T05:24:55.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"92bc7e947244515a404d99cd3ff0bcf138728656","tid":1975910,"uid":40542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T06:18:27.000Z","msg":"14：16高等法院手足還押就嚟100日🙇&zwj;♀🙇&zwj;♀要返工返學明，但全港係咪得15個人？🙇&zwj;♀"},{"pid":"dbc3e2401018d0dc998e86ed7b3ab832392b561e","tid":1975910,"uid":189132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T06:19:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\